description:
Watch this session recorded at Unreal Fest Orlando 2025 for a look at the innovative new functionality of Unreal Engine 5.6! 

This fast-paced presentation highlights the top new features in animation, rendering, VFX, and more.

Find out more about Unreal Engine 5.6 here: www.unrealengine.com/news/unreal-engine-5-6-is-now-available

author: Unreal Engine
description:
Watch this session recorded at Unreal Fest Orlando 2025 to hear all about advances in performance capture workflows in Unreal Engine. 

In this high-level overview of the new toolset released with UE5.6, you'll find out about motion capture workflow improvements and integrations with MetaHumans and MetaHuman Animator.

The session also includes a live demonstration showing the new workflow, including how to apply motion capture to MetaHumans.

Want to find out more about MetaHumans? Take a look here: www.metahuman.com
